@everyone

📣Big Update: Our First Agent-Powered Repository Is Live!

We’re excited to announce a major milestone for the Gen AI Global community!

<@673901899837341736>  has successfully built an agent capable of pulling and organizing chat content, and—alongside <@1143203059820933251> , <@546559083357143044> , and <@1352785241252565174> —developed our very first use case: a Resource Repository for our community.

This wouldn’t have been possible without our newly formed Web Development Team <@546559083357143044> , <@673901899837341736> , <@1352785241252565174> , <@1143203059820933251> , and <@1359551204648157214> —who just launched the foundational version of our website. 

<@546559083357143044>  led the UI development, ensuring the agent’s output is accessible and easy to navigate. While the site is still in its early stages, the agent-powered repository is already live and accessible as we continue building out the platform and adding more resources.

You can check out the repository here: https://genaiglobal.org/resources.html

⚠️Going forward, this will be the official home for all Gen AI Global resources.
If you’re looking for slides, guides, documentation, recordings, or key community tools—this is where you’ll find them⚠️

This channel will serve as the permanent access point to the repository, which will be updated regularly as our work evolves.

Bookmark it, use it, and share it—we’re building this for you.

Stay tuned—this is just the beginning!
